name: Couch Paper Roll
descr:
Non woven couch rolls, can be installed on either side of the table through our Rollholder. 60cm wide and 190 cm long.
Each roll is 40 meters long (include 20 pieces),
Asepsis is used to avoid bacterial infection and anaphylaxis of the body.

White color available only.
 
Packaging: 1 pcs/pack and 10 pack/1 box.
